Class Customer

java.lang.Object
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.User
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.Customer
All Implemented Interfaces:
customerManagement, Comparable<Customer>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Subscribed, Unsubscribed
public abstract class Customer extends User implements customerManagement, Comparable<Customer>
Represents a customer in the system. Customers can place orders and may have specific attributes depending on their subscription type. This abstract class extends the User class and implements customerManagement and Comparable.
Version:
23.0
Author:
Ferhat Kasim Koc
